00:02:39.460 --> 00:02:41.460
Six, they kill you with kindness

00:02:42.820 --> 00:02:49.469
Manipulators will try to be the nice guy or nice girl and do favors for you that make you feel pressured to return them on

00:02:49.630 --> 00:02:52.799
